  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK796">
<l>kēṭṭiṉu muṇṭō ruṟuti kiḷaiñarai</l>
<l>nīṭṭi yaḷappatōr kōl</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even in ruin there is some good; (for) it is a rod by which one may measure fully (the affection of one's) relations.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
